- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper mentions training computer vision methods from real examples, which involves machine learning techniques.
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is another possible category as the paper deals with video data and annotations.
- cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) is a possible category as the paper involves crowdsourcing the video creation process, which involves human interaction with computers.
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper mentions free-text descriptions and annotations, which are related to information retrieval tasks.
